<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>webpack 多页应用</title>
    <%= require(`../common/_meta.html`) %>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
            <h1 class="text--center">webpack 多页应用</h1>
            <ol>
                <li>集成了js、css、img压缩</li>
                <li class="o">编译es6、sass、vue</li>
                <li>自动添浏览器前缀postcss</li>
                <li>资源小于100时自动嵌入</li>
                <li>修改webpack.config自动重启webpack（$ npm start），js热更新，页面需改自动刷新 http://localhost:35729/livereload.js</li>
            </ol>

            <h3 class="text--center">图片引入</h3>
            <div class="box" style="width: 200px">
                <!-- 引入图片 -->
                <img class="img--fluid" src="<%= require(`assets/img/big.png`) %>" alt="">
            </div>

            <h3 class="text--center">vue引入</h3>
            <div id="app"></div>
            <%= require(`../common/vw.html`)  %>
                <%= require(`../common/rem.html`)  %>
                    <%= require(`../common/flex.html`)  %>
                        <%= require(`../common/icon.html`)  %>
                            <%= require(`../common/form.html`)  %>
                                <%= require(`../common/tab_line.html`)  %>
    </div>

    <!-- <% if(!htmlWebpackPlugin.options.env){ %> -->
